<h1><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Customizing Appearance</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/customizing-environment"><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Customizing Your Environment</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Customizing Appearance</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p>Since you will presumably be spending a fair amount of time working with <%= application.name %>, it is important to be able to customize the appearance of the user interface to your liking. <%= application.name %> offers a range of options for customizing the visual styles or "theme" that is used. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>Appearance Settings</h2>
			<p>The appearance is controlled through the <a href="#apps/theme-manager">Theme Manager</a> app.  To view and change the appearance settings, click on the second tab, labelled "Appearance". </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/appearance-settings.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title='Appearance" Tab on the System Settings App'><img class="dialog" src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/appearance-settings.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">"Appearance" Tab on the System Settings App</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-adjust"></i>Theme</h2>
			<p><%= application.name %> offers the ability to choose betweeen three different themes: </p>

			<ul>
				<li><label>Light</label> - a light, mostly monochrome theme. </li>
				<li><label>Standard</label> - a medium, blue accented theme. This is the default theme on non-mobile devices.</li>
				<li><label>Dark</label> - a dark, mostly monochrome theme. This is the default theme on mobile devices. </li>
			</ul>

			<div class="figure">
				<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/theme/standard-theme.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="The The Standard Theme"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/theme/standard-theme.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">The Standard Theme</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/theme/light-theme.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="The Light Theme"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/theme/light-theme.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">The Light Theme</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/theme/dark-theme.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="The Dark Theme"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/theme/dark-theme.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">The Dark Theme</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Style</h2>
			<p><%= application.name %> offers the ability to choose between two user interface styles: </p>
			<ul>
				<li><label>Opaque</label> - windows, menus and panels are opaque</li>
				<li><label>Transparent</label> - windows, menus, and panels are slightly transparent</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/style/opaque-style.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="The Opaque Style"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/style/opaque-style.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">The Opaque Style</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<a href="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/style/transparent-style.png" target="_blank" class="lightbox" title="The Transparent Style"><img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/style/transparent-style.png" /></a>
					<div class="caption">The Transparent Style</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-cube"></i>Material</h2>
			<p><%= application.name %> offers the ability to choose between several different materials.  Materials are used when rendering control elements such as window header bars, menus, buttons, tabs, and sliders. </p>

			<ul>
				<li><label>None</label> - constant color, flat shading</li>
				<li><label>Chalk</label> - diffuse shading only</li>
				<li><label>Plastic</label> - diffuse + highlights</li>
				<li><label>Glass</label> - transmitted + highlights</li>
				<li><label>Metal</label> - specular + highlights</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6" style="float:none">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/flat-tab.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/flat-slider.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/flat-buttons.png" />
					<div class="caption">No Material</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/chalk-tab.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/chalk-slider.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/chalk-buttons.png" />
					<div class="caption">The Chalk Material</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/plastic-tab.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/plastic-slider.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/plastic-buttons.png" />
					<div class="caption">The Plastic Material</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure row">
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/glass-tab.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/glass-slider.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/glass-buttons.png" />
					<div class="caption">The Glass Material</div>
				</div>
				<div class="figure col-sm-6">
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/metal-tab.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/metal-slider.png" />
					<img src="images/help/customizing-environment/customizing-appearance/material/metal-buttons.png" />
					<div class="caption">The Metal Material</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>